# Experiments and Artifacts

Each experiment script produces structured outputs under `artifacts/`.

## Experiment graph

```mermaid
flowchart LR
  A[baseline.py] --> B[baseline_results.json]
  A --> C[baseline.json]
  D[robustness.py] --> E[robustness_results.csv]
  D --> F[robustness_summary.json]
  G[calibration.py] --> H[calibration_results.json]
  G --> I[roc_*.png / pr_*.png]
  J[tfidf_ablation.py] --> K[tfidf_ablation_results.csv]
  J --> L[tfidf_ablation_summary.json]
  M[cross_dataset.py] --> N[cross_dataset_results.json]
  M --> O[errors_*.csv]
  M --> P[analysis_notes.md]
```

## Outputs by purpose

- **Metrics**: JSON/CSV summaries for comparison and reporting
- **Diagnostics**: error samples and cross-dataset analysis notes
- **Visualization**: ROC/PR plots and notebook charts
